page_content: Intel CPU Intel® Xeon® série Max 9460 with 40 cores and 80 threads, 350 W TDP, supports DDR5 with max memory speed of 4800 MT/s 1DPC or 4400 MT/s 2DPC across 8 memory channels, and PCIe 5.0 with 80 lanes. It was released in Q1'23, runs at a base clock of 2.20 GHz and boosts up to 3.50 GHz. Peak performance is 11264.0 GFLOPS. It is priced at $8750.00.
